OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening to end Sunday, however cloud
OL,7,Fwill build from the north with showery
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain reaching the region
OL,9,Fby dawn. Winds falling light and
OL,10,Ffeeling chilly under the clearest
OL,11,Fskies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,14,Fsink south across the West Midlands
OL,15,Fduring Monday morning, clearing to
OL,16,Fsunny spells into the afternoon.
OL,17,FFeeling rather chilly for the time of
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
